.B ci.commentsHeight
height of the comments window.
.tp
.B ci.diffHeight
height of the diffs window (the lower window).
.tp
.B ci.display_bytes
Number of bytes to show in new files in
.BR "bk citool" .
If set to 0, the entire
file is displayed. Default:\ 8192
.tp
.B ci.editHeight
Height of the popup editor.  Default:\ 30
.tp
