.tp
.B fm3.toggleAnnotations
Keyboard accelerator for toggling the display of annotations.
Default:\ \*(lqz\*(rq.
.tp
.B fm3.toggleGCA
Keyboard accelerator for toggling the display of the GCA.
Default:\ \*(lqx\*(rq.
.tp
.B fm3.undo
Keyboard accelerator for undoing the last merge selection.
Default:\ \*(lqu\*(rq.
